  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230410/extras/643cf82bc62a5faf72e863968b00ac93.poster.avif?t=1613643100\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230410/extras/643cf82bc62a5faf72e863968b00ac93.webm?t=1613643100\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230410/extras/643cf82bc62a5faf72e863968b00ac93.mp4?t=1613643100\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Chaos is an online FPS game. <br>Why should you play it? <br>Destruction, lots of it, plus some explosions, oh yeah, guns! <br>Who doesn't like guns and explosions? <br>that's what Chaos is all about...<br><br>Official Discord: <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1230410/extras/c0bc929a88faa4504d081927cf00b43c.avif?t=1613643100\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br>The main features of Chaos are:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fight AI In The New Arena Mode!<br></li><li> Sliding<br></li><li> Wall Jumping<br></li><li> Ground Slam<br></li><li> Dynamic Crosshair System<br></li><li> (Almost) Fully Destructible Environments<br></li><li> Grenade to Blow Holes In Walls, And To Push The Player<br></li><li> Fast-Paced Gameplay<br></li><li> Lots Of Weapons <br>    M4A1<br>    AKM<br>    SMLE MKIII<br>    MP5<br>    Semi-Auto Shotgun<br>    Sniper<br>    Rocket Launcher<br>    Kriss Vector<br>    Hush Puppy<br>    M249<br>    Katana<br>    Grenade Launcher<br>    More To Come...<br></li><li> Lots Of Modes<br>    Free For All<br>    Team Deathmatch<br>    Free For All Permadeath (200% HP)<br></li><li> Lots Of Maps With Unique Twists<br>    Space<br>    Lava<br>    Floating Missiles<br></li><li> Accurate Linetrace Based Gunplay<br></li><li> Built From Trusted Feedback </li></ul>",
